sentence.text: However, there was no research elucidating the genetic association of entire positive regulation of cholesterol transport pathway with ovarian cancer susceptibility.
Therefore, we conducted genotyping for 17 SNPs of six NER core genes (XPA, XPC, XPG, nucleotide-excision repair, ERCC2, and ERCC4) in 89 ovarian cancer cases and 356 cancer-free controls.
